node.text: I was only seven years old when I saw it for the first time. I have no idea how many hundreds of times I have seen this movie since, or how many times I made my kids watch it over the years, but I often watch it when I’m feeling like I need to be cheered up or I need to feel warm and fuzzy and safe. It makes me really happy and I love all the lessons it teaches along the way. It’s probably why I grew up wanting to have a really big family. I’m so sad to hear today of the passing of Christopher Plummer… One of the things he often said was what a wonderful life he’s had. My love thoughts and prayers go out to his family and my gratitude and appreciation for all the wonderful roles he played and how he always made me feel when I watched the sound of music... God rest his soul 🙏❤️

node.title: The sound of music is my favorite movie.

You have always been my greatest inspiration, the one I can come to for anything, and if it weren’t for your love, support and guidance, I wouldn’t be the woman or the mother I am today. Thank you being our rock. You are the greatest mother, grandmother, friend and mentor. I thank God every day for choosing you to be my mom. Thank you for all you do for me and for our family. I love you more than you’ll ever know. Xo

Dose & Co NEW collagen beauty tablets launching today in @walmart !! @khloekardashian @doseandco ✨💗 #repost @khloekardashian

Say hello to our newest product: Dose & Co Collagen Beauty Tablets, launching into @Walmart today 🤍

Our Collagen Beauty Tablets are made using an active blend of collagen, biotin and vitamin C for unmatched skin, hair and nail support.

Each serving includes 3 grams of collagen, taken easily on the go.

​ ✨Type 1 & type 3 collagen
​ ✨Free from sugar, gluten, GMOs, & fillers
​ ✨Keto-friendly
​ ✨100% recyclable packaging
​
​*Available only in the USA

node.text: Happy Birthday beautiful @cicibussey!! You are such a special and important part of my family and I have been blessed beyond measure with your love and friendship for the last 46 years!!! You are an amazing cousin, friend, auntie, sister, wife daughter, confidant and best friend and I love you so much! Thank you for being there for all of us through thick and thin… and for sharing all of our amazing memories together. I love you!!!!!!! 😍❤️🙏🥰🎂🥳

node.text: Love this!! Kate Moss for @skims!! #repost @kimkardashian Introducing Kate Moss for @SKIMS. I first met @katemossagency in 2014 through Ricardo Tisci, and was instantly struck by her cheeky humor, authentic and classic beauty - we’ve been friends ever since! She is THE fashion icon, defining a whole generation of style and I am honored to feature her as the new face of SKIMS this Summer! 📷 @donnatrope
